### Health check
GET http://localhost:4001/api/health

### List predictive alerts
GET http://localhost:4001/api/predictive-alerts

### Generate rule-based alerts from tree health records
POST http://localhost:4001/api/predictive-alerts/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Defer alert
PATCH http://localhost:4001/api/predictive-alerts/ALT-002/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "deferred"
}

### Approve alert and create maintenance task
POST http://localhost:4001/api/predictive-alerts/ALT-001/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ranger": "Ahmad Razif"
}

### List created maintenance tasks
GET http://localhost:4001/api/tasks
